headline: Hormel Foods (HRL) Appoints Jeffrey Ettinger as Interim CEO, John Ghingo as President
summary: Hormel Foods Corporation (NYSE:HRL) is one of the best alternative meat stocks to invest in according to analysts. On June 23, the company announced the appointment of Jeffrey M. Ettinger as interim CEO and John Ghingo as President. Ghingo’s promotion makes him the 11th individual to hold this position in the company’s nearly 135-year history. […]

headline: Here's What to Expect From Hormel Foods' Next Earnings Report
summary: Hormel Foods is expected to release its third-quarter earnings in September, with analysts anticipating low double-digit bottom-line growth.
